cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with the task of interactive image retrieval using natural language queries, which involves computer vision (CV) and natural language processing (NLP) techniques. Therefore, cs.CV and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a new framework for encoding multiple queries, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, making cs.AI a likely sub-category. The paper also evaluates its proposed method on two benchmarks, which involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (ML) techniques, making cs.IR and cs.LG likely sub-categories as well.
